name: Winchester High School
directions: Through the front entrance, past the auditorium/cafeteria/band wing, left in the gym/tech wing. They'll be on your left, labeled; there are two of them.
comment:
Student/staff use only, unless you're a parent who can gain entry. Locks don't work; I'd advise knocking before entering and placing a backpack by the door when you're in. Keep in mind it's by all the sports centers, so you might want to exercise caution going in/out. 
If you're a student, I'd advise going before/after school or during lunch; it takes forever to get from any classes to the restrooms, since they're pretty far from most of the actual academic wings, and you don't want to have to explain to your teachers why it's taking you seven entire minutes just to use the bathroom, particularly if you're closeted.
